  <!-- EN: desired -->
  <VME_PermanentBases_Desired.label>渴望</VME_PermanentBases_Desired.label>
  <!-- EN: Our colony should become our forever home, the more buildings, paths, and lights we can erect the better off we’ll all be.\n\n<color=#E5E54C>Gameplay effect:</color>\n - Colonists gets mood penalties / bonuses depending on amount of buildings on the map. "Building" is a completely enclosed structure with at least 25 tiles size. -->
  <VME_PermanentBases_Desired.description>我们的殖民地应该成为永恒的家园。我们建造的房屋、道路与照明灯越多，我们也就过得越舒适。\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C&gt;游戏效果：&lt;/color&gt;\n - 殖民者会依据地图上的房屋数量来获得心情减益/增益。“房屋”的空间面积必须不少于25格。</VME_PermanentBases_Desired.description>
  <!-- EN: Magnificent city (more than 20 buildings) -->
  <VME_PermanentBases_Desired.comps.0.thoughtStageDescriptions.0>宏伟的城镇（房屋数量超过20）</VME_PermanentBases_Desired.comps.0.thoughtStageDescriptions.0>
