  <VME_PermanentBases_Desired.comps.0.thoughtStageDescriptions.1>美丽的城镇（房屋数量少于20）</VME_PermanentBases_Desired.comps.0.thoughtStageDescriptions.1>
  <!-- EN: Many beautiful buildings (less than 15 buildings) -->
  <VME_PermanentBases_Desired.comps.0.thoughtStageDescriptions.2>温馨的城镇（房屋数量少于15）</VME_PermanentBases_Desired.comps.0.thoughtStageDescriptions.2>
  <!-- EN: Burgeoning city (less than 10 buildings) -->
  <VME_PermanentBases_Desired.comps.0.thoughtStageDescriptions.3>新兴的城镇（房屋数量少于10）</VME_PermanentBases_Desired.comps.0.thoughtStageDescriptions.3>
  <!-- EN: Not enough buildings (less than 5 buildings) -->
