  <!-- EN: despised -->
  <VME_PermanentBases_Despised.label>厌恶</VME_PermanentBases_Despised.label>
  <!-- EN: Our colony is only temporary, should we stay it will only be a matter of time before we are unable to defend it, it is better to never gain such comfort.\n\n<color=#E5E54C>Stats:</color>\n - Farming yield: -10%.\n - Gathering yield: +40%. -->
  <VME_PermanentBases_Despised.description>殖民地并非我们长久的居所，就算留下来也无法永远守卫它。我们最好不要对此抱有幻想。\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C&gt;状态：&lt;/color&gt;\n - 农耕产量：-10%。\n - 远行采集量：+40%。</VME_PermanentBases_Despised.description>
